"'''Shape-shifters'''" was an article for [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]] that was published in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 12|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 12]]. It was written by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and illustrated by [[Steve Bryant]], and provided details on four [[Changeling/Legends|shapeshifting]] [[Species/Legends|species]]: the [[Protean]]s, [[Polydroxol]], [[Stennes]] Shifters, and [[Shi'ido]].

